Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The dreams embraced by a single life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}are boundless beyond even the stars.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The dreams that we foster over time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}are waiting for the moment{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}when we come upon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.53,0:00:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The words we exchange{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}make our hearts tremble,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}and a chance meeting{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}could change the future.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}People, no matter who they are,{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}as they pursue their dreams,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}have the courage to travel new paths.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}As we leave behind a living{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}testament of our journey,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}the Galaxy Railways on which{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}we travel continue ever on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.18,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Men have certain thoughts{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}that cannot easily be swayed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}As they lie hidden{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}within their hearts,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}they occasionally give rise to{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}irreconcilable conflicts with others.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Once again, a new destiny{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}is starting to form...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I am Yuuki Manabu, and as of today,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I am assigned to Sirius Platoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Please, accept my regards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"The Driving Wheel of Fate"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I told you to hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You hear me!? Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bring me the money,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}or I'll kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't get the idea that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}this is some hollow threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}How many times have you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}lost your life now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You only get one real life, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't go slacking off just\N{\c&He1e1e1&}because this is a simulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Even if it is by the captain's orders,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I have no intention of hanging around,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}training some new member\N{\c&He1e1e1&}who doesn't have any drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Go have Yuki take care of you at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes? Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.52,0:04:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.52,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Uh, Yuki-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}san{\i0}, please don't be so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is the manual. See that\N{\c&He1e1e1&}you commit it to memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Watch yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're the ones who appeared\N{\c&He1e1e1&}out of nowhere, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's a pretty brave tone\N{\c&He1e1e1&}for a weepy little girl to take
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}with the SDF's Vega Platoon,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the greatest in the universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're a new member of\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're a pretty plucky chick, huh?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Care to join Vega Platoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sure. If I ever get dismissed from\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.85,0:05:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If she's ever dismissed, she says!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Bunch of creeps.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.53,0:05:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is there someone still\N{\c&He1e1e1&}inside the simulation room?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Pretty diligent of you, Yuuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Can I help you out? I've already\N{\c&He1e1e1&}finished today's training.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're going at it at this high a level?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.88,0:05:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}T- the higher the level you train\N{\c&He1e1e1&}at, the faster you improve, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.56,0:05:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not put together the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}same way as some people,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}who graduate first from their\N{\c&He1e1e1&}training schools, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Oh, did I touch a nerve? I'm sorry,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I shouldn't have said it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I was just thinking that if you're\N{\c&He1e1e1&}thinking this hard, Yuuki-{\i1}kun{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}then I'd better stick to it as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The sort of grades I had in\N{\c&He1e1e1&}training school don't mean anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}now that I'm out in the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}real world. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to stop here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.26,0:06:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If I overdo it and ruin my\N{\c&He1e1e1&}health, that won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.19,0:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Well, shall we go get some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.87,0:06:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll pass today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}I hadn't realized it was{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}set at such a high level.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.88,0:06:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}What on earth was Bruce trying to do?{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Was it to get me to improve?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.55,0:06:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Didn't he know what a high level it{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}was set at? Or was it something else...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Incoming emergency transmission!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A hijacking incident has occurred on the\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No.620 Express{\i0}, on the Kaitos-Sigma Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The culprit appears to be holding\N{\c&He1e1e1&}some of the passengers hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.51,0:07:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Receiving request to dispatch the SDF.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.85,0:07:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Order Spica Platoon into action!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have them ascertain the situation,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}and gather more information!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.19,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Spica Platoon, copy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Excuse me, you there...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You there! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't make that gloomy face.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Drink this, and take heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}U- um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're Wataru-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s son, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your face resembles your father's.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Your father was a good man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.89,0:08:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't know what happened,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}but don't let it get you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We've had an emergency call\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to action. Return at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.83,0:08:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Good luck to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}System check!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}System check, standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Particle warpspeed\N{\c&He1e1e1&}generators reading normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Orbital communications\N{\c&He1e1e1&}radar reading normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.85,0:08:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0} moving to launch position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Ascent Float lock confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Gravitational barrier\N{\c&He1e1e1&}generator systems normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.20,0:08:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Energy normal. Pressure within the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}boiler is rising. Cylinder valves open.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.21,0:08:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Engage main circuits.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Systems all green!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}Big One{\i0}, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The incident has taken place aboard the\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}No.620 Express{\i0}, on the Kaitos-Sigma Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The culprit's demands are to bring him\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the girlfriend that broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry up and bring Catherine here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}U-um, sure, just calm down, please!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}There's no need to rough up the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Listen to me! Do not stop this train!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}If you stop, I'll kill these people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}He's not giving the SDF enough credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Commence searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.87,0:09:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:10:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}According to the information\N{\c&He1e1e1&}gathered by Spica Platoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}the culprit has lost the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}capacity for normal reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.21,0:10:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Taking the safety of the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}passengers into consideration,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}stopping the train would be too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I would also like to avoid him\N{\c&He1e1e1&}realizing that we've transferred aboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}And so, here is the plan:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.56,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis, posing as the culprit's girlfriend,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}will approach in a combat shuttle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David, you accompany her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You two buy as much time as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}While you're at it, {\i1}Big One{\i0} will\N{\c&He1e1e1&}approach {\i1}No. 620{\i0} from the rear,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}so as not to be detected by the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.24,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce, Yuuki, you will board {\i1}No. 620{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Once inside, you will both quickly\N{\c&He1e1e1&}move to the car he has taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}When the timing is right, charge in at\N{\c&He1e1e1&}once from both the front and rear doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.89,0:10:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and take control of the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I will remain aboard {\i1}Big{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&\i1}One{\i0} and direct everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.93,0:10:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not about to board\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that train with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why can't you stand the sight of me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Have I done anything wrong to you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}To put it frankly, I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Your old man was Captain, and your\N{\c&He1e1e1&}brother was a Panzer Grenadier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.55,0:11:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm sure you're here on the\N{\c&He1e1e1&}pretense of carrying on their work,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}or for some other laudable reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}but this is no place where you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}can get by being starstruck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.89,0:11:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not going to place my life\N{\c&He1e1e1&}in the hands of some Mama's boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I think I know how tough it is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.56,0:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What do you know!? What does a tenderfoot\N{\c&He1e1e1&}like you know about the SDF, huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stop that, Bruce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.91,0:11:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There will be no change in plans.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}68 minutes until we link up with {\i1}No. 620{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All hands, outfit yourselves with\N{\c&He1e1e1&}first class equipment, and standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}This is Spica Platoon.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Looks like it's your turn, at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're grateful for your\N{\c&He1e1e1&}information scans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Okay then, we're counting\N{\c&He1e1e1&}on you to do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon, best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Data transfer from\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Spica Platoon complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Sirius Platoon, we will\N{\c&He1e1e1&}now commence operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Launch preparations complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I've brought Catherine. We're going\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to come aboard. Lower your shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.89,0:13:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Catherine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.89,0:13:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}R- right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}T- this is {\i1}No. 620{\i0}... Galaxy Railways\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Administration, please lower the shields!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis, pretend you're scared.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Buy as much time as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Isn't she here yet!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is she doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't need anyone who's going\N{\c&He1e1e1&}to slow me down! Head back, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm not going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:15:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I won't save you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Bruce and Yuuki are aboard.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Louis, the ruse is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Did it look like my knees were knocking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Are you sure you really weren't\N{\c&He1e1e1&}too scared to come across?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Do I look like that sort of feeble woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Why hasn't Catherine come here!?\N{\c&He1e1e1&}She's on the train, isn't she!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm going to go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shut up! Keep that damned baby quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}There, there, please, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}David, aren't you there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}One more car...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.18,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shut him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I told you to keep him quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.52,0:16:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No! Please, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Hey! You hear me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}All right. Rush him in thirty seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.19,0:16:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Let him go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Give Thomas back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Thomas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Don't do anything foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Shut up! I'm going to\N{\c&He1e1e1&}make this brat shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.53,0:16:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll kill him! Stay back!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}You stay back! I'll kill you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.54,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}SDF!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Keep back! Keep back, or I'll kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.22,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Attention, passengers, you're\N{\c&He1e1e1&}all right now. Please calm down,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}and slowly move to the rearward cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That was crazy, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}The SDF is not a death squadron! If you\N{\c&He1e1e1&}mean to commit suicide, go somewhere else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.87,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}We're finished settling\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the passengers back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}san{\i0}! Don't move!\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I'll get you some first aid at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}It doesn't shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No. It's an FW306. That's the model\N{\c&He1e1e1&}the SDF used to use a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.85,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}That gun is the one my\N{\c&He1e1e1&}predecessor, Captain Yuuki, used.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.19,0:18:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Salute Captain Yuuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Mamoru... Manabu...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}My sons, once you become adults, and set{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}forth across this vast sea of space,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}think of your father,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}and show me your valiant spirits.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.21,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Kanna, this time, it looks like\N{\c&He1e1e1&}I will be gone a long while...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yuuki-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yo, you're back, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}You're already better?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah. That's the SDF for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}They've got the most advanced\N{\c&He1e1e1&}medical equipment and technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No matter how state-of-the-art they are,\N{\c&He1e1e1&}they can't bring a dead person back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.87,0:19:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:19:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}A gun that doesn't work is\N{\c&He1e1e1&}worse than a security blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}I don't want it. I don't need a\N{\c&He1e1e1&}gun to help people in this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you think you can get buy with\N{\c&He1e1e1&}that utopian attitude of yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}then leave the SDF right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}If you wish to stay, then carry this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Is that an order?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Understood. I will carry it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.58,0:20:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}But I will not use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The time when you will have to use it{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}will come, in order for you to survive.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}That is the law of the universe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}As two thoughts pass by each{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}other, where do they run off to?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Nobody can yet see where{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}their terminal station is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}Irregularity detected at Alpha Centauri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}No identification number.\N{\c&He1e1e1&}Affiliation unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}How many nights have I{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}spent alone since then?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:22:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Constantly having dreams of the hope{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}that you are, as I lightly sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.90,0:22:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The smiles and tears that{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}you gave to me and me alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.91,0:22:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}come to mind every time{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}I get disheartened,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.25,0:22:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}and I set forth again toward the morrow.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}The joyful light of{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}the galaxy beckons me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.53,0:22:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}to that beloved person within my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}No matter how far apart we are,{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}my memories will never fade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:23:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}My heart wishes always{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}to be at your side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.50,0:23:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&He1e1e1&}"Next Episode Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.57,0:23:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}A planet where night falls{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}only once every three months...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}A pitch-black train,{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}with no last stop...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.24,0:23:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}What lies at the end of{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}its journey into darkness?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.91,0:23:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}Tales of the Galaxy Railways, Episode 4:{\i0}\N{\c&He1e1e1&}"Those Who Call Themselves Eternal"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.58,0:23:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}We're going to encounter{\i0}\N{\i1\c&He1e1e1&}something at the next station.{\i0}